      <h3>6.6 DATA SETS(within DEVICE TABS</h3>
 
      <p>
        Select which device's data you would like to show up when you are using the Custom Graphing tool.
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>Choose "Configuration" from the Main Menu.</li>
        <li>Click the specific device tab you wish to edit.</li>
        <li>Select and deselect data points to "Display in Graphing?" - the selected points will allow for quick custom graphing.</li>
      </ol>
      <br>
